'''Igjda n Herkulis''' (s [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tmaziɣt]]: ⵉⴳⵊⴷⴰ ⵏ ⵀⵉⵔⴽⵓⵍⵉⵙ, s [[Tutlayt Talatint|tlatint]]: Columnae Herculis, s [[Tutlayt Tagrikt|tgrikt]]: Ἡράκλειαι Στῆλαι ''Erákleiai Stílai'') nɣ '''Igjda n Waṭlas''' iga ism azayku lli tn ikkan ɣ uzmz n ayt tagrikt. Ar sis tqṣaḍn idrarn s sin lli illan ɣ tmi n [[Urupa]] ɣ iffus d [[Tafriqt]] ɣ ugafa, ad tn t igan: [[Adrar n Musa]] (nɣ ''Adrar n Abyla'' s yism nns azayku) ɣ ugafa n tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]], d [[Adrar n Djabal Ṭariq|Aẓru n Djabal Ṭariq]] lli itabɛan i [[Lingliz]].

Kkan-tt-inn irumiyn n uzmz azayku skrn ɣ '''Igjda n Herkulis''' zund kran iwtta gr umaḍal lli ɣ tlla taɣrma (ma mu ttinin s tlatint: ''Mare nostrum'') d yill Aṭlasi s ɣinna lli icqqan.

== Amzruy ==
[[Afaylu:Tarifa, Estrecho de Gibraltar. Strait of Gibraltar.jpg|thumb|245x245px|[[Adrar n Musa]], yan zɣ Igjda n Herkuli lli illan ɣ tfriqt ugafa, ittuyẓrran zɣ Tarifa, ɣ tsga yaḍni n Djabal Tariq.]]

=== Mad ttinin irumiyn ===
Lliɣ yumẓ [[Herkulis]] aɣaras nns s ugdal n [[Hespiridis|Hesperides]] ɣ ammas n tgzirt n [[Iritya]]. Ikka-tt-inn ḍaruri ixṣṣa ad izri f yan udrar ikka-tt-inn iga s yism Aṭlas, ɣ udɣar ayɣli s udrar ann, iga yas tazmrt icqqan nns afad ad izri udrar ann zɣ tuẓẓumt nns at lliɣ d iffuɣ ɣ tsga yaḍni n udrar. S tɣarast ad as ismun [[Herkulis]] yill [[Ill Agrakal|agrakal]] d yill aṭlasi tiklt tamzwarut d iskr ma mu nttini ɣila [[Imi n Djabal Ṭariq]]. Ɣayad ar aɣ ittini zɛma mas [[Adrar n Musa]] d [[Izig n Djabal Ṭariq]] gan ɣar ɣaylli d iciḍn zɣ idrar azayku n Aṭlas.<ref>Seneca, Hercules Furens 235ff.; Seneca, Hercules Oetaeus 1240; Pliny, Nat. Hist. iii.4.</ref>

=== Mad ittini Diodorus ===
Diodore Siculus, yan unmezruy agrik, ikka-tt-inn ar ittals mas [[Herkulis]] ismun iftasn n [[Imi n Djabal Ṭariq]] lli tn yad ikkan mac ikka-tt-inn iwsɛa bzzaf (urd zund ɣaylli ttinin irumiyn) bac ad ur yajj imẓiwn n yill aṭlasi ad kcmn s yill [[Ill Agrakal|agrakal]].<ref>Diodorus 4.18.5</ref>

